  "prompt": "What are some good movies about a person that has a hidden power that he/she couldn't use until put into a pressure situation?",
  "response": "There are several intriguing movies in which characters discover hidden powers under pressure. Here are some recommendations across various genres:\n\n1. **\"Chronicle\" (2012)** - This film follows three high school friends who acquire telekinetic abilities after encountering a mysterious object. Their powers grow as they face various situations, leading to tension and conflict.\n\n2. **\"The Matrix\" (1999)** - Neo, a computer hacker, discovers his true identity and abilities as \"The One\" who can manipulate the simulated reality known as the Matrix. His powers become evident when he is put under intense pressure.\n\n3. **\"Unbreakable\" (2000)** - Directed by M. Night Shyamalan, this film stars Bruce Willis as a man who begins to uncover his superhuman strengths after surviving a devastating accident.\n\n4. **\"Lucy\" (2014)** - Scarlett Johansson stars as a woman who inadvertently gains powerful cognitive and physical abilities following exposure to a synthetic drug. Her abilities intensify in critical situations.\n\n5. **\"Push\" (2009)** - This sci-fi thriller features characters with various psychic abilities, including a protagonist who must tap into his hidden powers to defeat a covert government agency.\n\n6. **\"X-Men: First Class\" (2011)** - While many X-Men films explore the concept of hidden powers, this prequel highlights characters like Charles Xavier and Erik Lehnsherr as they discover and hone their mutant abilities under duress.\n\n7. **\"The Incredibles\" (2004)** - In this animated film, members of a superhero family must come out of hiding and reveal their superpowers to protect the world from a new threat.\n\n8. **\"Kung Fu Hustle\" (2004)** - This action-comedy showcases a hapless gangster who unexpectedly unlocks his profound martial arts talents when faced with overwhelming odds.\n\nThese films present a variety of settings and styles, offering engaging stories where characters uncover their true potential when faced with challenging or dangerous situations.",
